data.description: GREAT HOME with over 2100 square feet, 4 bedrooms and 2 and half bathrooms.  Master suite is on the main floor with a walk in closet, double sinks and a garden tub. Wonderful living room with laminate flooring, high ceilings and fireplace.   Really nice covered back patio that makes a great entertaining area.  Spacious kitchen with an island and nice pantry for lots of storage.  Stucco exterior and a 3 car attached garage.
